data.description: NO HIGH ELECTRIC BILLS on this Beautiful Historic Home!  3 bedrooms 2 baths down stairs with a Master suite upstairs.  If you Love Old Homes, these Hardwood floors and high ceilings and old fireplaces and front porch give this home the Southern Charm it needs to stand out in the community.  Beautiful 1.8 acre beautiful lot with fenced back yard.  This home is beautiful!  Come and sit on the long front porch and enjoy the small town atmosphere. SELLER PROVIDING a NEW 4 Point Inspection and New Wind Mitigation Report.
